{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Gamepad.id","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Gamepad/id","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Gamepad_API\">Gamepad API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Gamepad\"><code>Gamepad</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Gamepad/axes\"><code>axes</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Gamepad/buttons\"><code>buttons</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Gamepad/connected\"><code>connected</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Gamepad/displayId\"><code>displayId</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Gamepad/hand\"><code>hand</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Gamepad/hapticActuators\"><code>hapticActuators</code></a></li><li><em><code>id</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Gamepad/index\"><code>index</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Gamepad/mapping\"><code>mapping</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Gamepad/pose\"><code>pose</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Gamepad/timestamp\"><code>timestamp</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Gamepad/vibrationActuator\"><code>vibrationActuator</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Gamepad API に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/GamepadButton\"><code>GamepadButton</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/GamepadEvent\"><code>GamepadEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Navigator/getGamepads\"><code>Navigator.getGamepads()</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Gamepad\"><code>Gamepad</code></a> インターフェースの<strong> <code>Gamepad.id</code></strong> プロパティはコントローラーに関するいくつかの情報を含む文字列を返します。</p>\n\n<p><span class=\"tlid-translation translation\"><span title=\"\">正確な構文は厳密には指定されていませんが、Firefox では3つの情報がダッシュ&nbsp;</span></span>(<code>-</code>)<span class=\"tlid-translation translation\"><span title=\"\"> で区切られています</span></span> :</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><span class=\"tlid-translation translation\"><span title=\"\">USBベンダーとコントローラーの製品IDを含む</span></span>2つの4桁16進数字列</li>\n <li><span class=\"tlid-translation translation\"><span title=\"\">ドライバーが提供するコントローラーの名前</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>例えば、PS2 のコントローラーは <strong>810-3-USB Gamepad</strong> を返します。</p>\n\n<p><span class=\"tlid-translation translation\"><span title=\"\">この情報は、デバイス上のコントロールのマッピングを見つけたり、ユーザーに有用なフィードバックを表示したりすることを目的としています。</span></span></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"構文","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><span class=\"idlInterface\" id=\"idl-def-Gamepad\"><span class=\"idlAttribute\">readonly    attribute <span class=\"idlAttrType\">DOMString</span>           <span class=\"idlAttrName\">id</span>;</span></span></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"gamepadconnected\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> gp <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> navigator<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getGamepads</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  gamepadInfo<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>innerHTML <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Gamepad connected at index \"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> gp<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>index <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">\": \"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> gp<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>id <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">\".\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"値","title":"値","isH3":false,"content":"<p><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"この項目についての文書はまだ書かれていません。書いてみませんか？\"><code>string</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"仕様","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">コメント</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/gamepad/#widl-Gamepad-id\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Gamepad<br><small lang=\"ja\">Gamepad.id の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">草案</span></td>\n   <td>初版</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザの互換性","id":"ブラウザの互換性","isH3":false,"query":"api.Gamepad.id","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Gamepad/id/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参照","title":"参照","isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Gamepad_API/Using_the_Gamepad_API\">Gamepad API の利用</a></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"構文"},{"text":"例","id":"例"},{"text":"値","id":"値"},{"text":"仕様","id":"仕様"},{"text":"ブラウザの互換性","id":"ブラウザの互換性"},{"text":"参照","id":"参照"}],"summary":"Gamepad インターフェースの Gamepad.id プロパティはコントローラーに関するいくつかの情報を含む文字列を返します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Gamepad.id","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Gamepad.id","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/gamepad/id","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/gamepad/id/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Gamepad","title":"Gamepad"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Gamepad/id","title":"Gamepad.id"}],"pageTitle":"Gamepad.id - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}